what to do when death for me death is not an option unless of course its just my time to go but i won't take my own life life is precious and my family would miss me at the same time i feel nothing but despair like i'm trapped in a box of hopelessness i'm afraid to be happy because it only leads to a letdown i cause my family worry and pain i always feel guilty and worthless how can i live when life is like this try to see a doctor asap there are so many resources such as psychologists psychiatrists and even medications that will get you out of your depression if that is not an option call up a friend or family member and tell them that you just need to talk to someone you may also try starting a journal write down how you are feeling daily whether it is good or bad it helps so much to get your thoughts and fears off your mind and when you are feeling better you can look back at your journal and be proud of your progress you acknowledge that life is precious and that your family would be upset etc let them help you with what is bringing you down you are right life is precious your life is precious and so is your quality of life put yourself first and take care of you use the resources you have for help hopefully you will be back on the road to happiness very soon good luck Sigmund Freud Anxiety Suicide Darwin from Insectivorous plants to Worms Social rule Transsexuality Milton H. Erickson Prostate cancer Procrastination Psychiatric hospital Pitaten One Tree Hill (TV series) Psychiatry Scientology beliefs and practices Love and Theft Goodness and value theory Divorce Charles Darwin's illness Pok__mon Live! Bipolar disorder Post-traumatic stress disorder EastEnders Characters in the Smurfs Fathers' rights Care Bears Sydney Riot of 1879 Cult Grief Theory of conduct Series finale Self-harm Obsessive-compulsive disorder Knots Landing Psychoanalysis Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Anorexia nervosa Teenage suicide Breastfeeding Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Insomnia Clinical depressi